refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;


 &style.oop;


 public static arrayIntlCalendar::getAvailableLocales




 &style.procedural;


 arrayintlcal_get_available_locales




 Gives the list of locales for which calendars are installed. As of ICU 51,
 this is the list of all installed ICU locales.

&reftitle.examples;
IntlCalendar::getAvailableLocales
<?php print_r(IntlCalendar::getAvailableLocales());
&example.outputs;
Array ( [0] => af [1] => af_NA [2] => af_ZA [3] => agq [4] => agq_CM [5] => ak [6] => ak_GH [7] => am [8] => am_ET [9] => ar [10] => ar_001 [11] => ar_AE [12] => ar_BH [13] => ar_DJ … output abbreviated … [595] => zh_Hant_HK [596] => zh_Hant_MO [597] => zh_Hant_TW [598] => zu [599] => zu_ZA )
